15. e5!? {[%mdl 32768]} ( { I think that this move is the most challenging as White builds a strong center and makes Bg7 really bad. On the other hand, however, Black has now nice control over the light squares so there is this trade-off. Still, I think it is White's best chance. } 15.Kg1 { is another decent option that definitely can be tried too. However, I like } ) ( 15.e5 { - I believe it poses serious practical problems to Black. } ) Nc4!? { It makes sense to activate the knight with a tempo. This was also suggested in the Peter Svidler's course on Grunfeld and I must admit, it is a pretty good line and it took me a long time to find something that I actually liked and felt comfortable recommending. } 
