12. h4!? {[%mdl 32768]} { A typical idea in these positions, but again, after the queen moved to c7, h4 acquires additional strength as ...e5 or ...e6 does not allow the queen to go to the kingside. } e6! { I believe that this is the only move here after which Black is not much worse. The idea is... to bring the queen to e7! This already proves that the Qc7 line cannot be good. } ( 12...Bd7? { is even worse than ...Bg4-Bd7. } 13.h5 $16 ) 
