19. c4 { I think that this could be the best try for White. Even though the position is approximately equal, it is not so easy to play for Black. This is also what Sjugirov played. Engines claim equality here, but due to Black's mistake, White got a much better position very quickly. For a detailed explanation of White's alternatives, see here. [/variation/21328445/#/19/w] } Qh4! 
20. Qd3! {[%cal Gd3a3][%csl Gc4]} ( { Right now, we can't play } 20.Nc3 { due to } 20...Qxc4 { . This move protects the c-pawn and prepares Qa3. } ) Rfe8 
