16. hxg4 {[%mdl 32768]} Ne5 
17. Bb4! {[%csl Ra3,Re7]} { The point - the e7-pawn falls. } Qxa2 ( 17...Qd3 18.Bxe7 Rfe8 19.Rb7 $14 { is also not easy for Black. } ) 
18. Nc3 Qa6 
19. Bxe7 { Here, Black has only one good move. } Rfb8□ ( { Black must try to simplify the position and install a blockade with ...Nd7 in the future. With correct play, Black is fine here, but getting there and navigating through such complicated lines is not easy at all. } 19...Rfe8 20.d6+- { is winning for White - Black has zero counterplay. } ) 
20. d6!? ( 20.Ra1 Qb7 21.d6 Nd7 22.Nd5 a5! $13 { is less clear. } ) Rxb1 
21. Qxb1 Nd7 
