14. Rb4 Nxc4 
15. Rxc4 Bb5 
16. Rc5! -- ( { White has just an extra pawn and Black does not have sufficient compensation. } 16...Rc8 { Black needs to accept that capturing the d4-pawn is not a thing. } 17.Rxc8 Qxc8 18.a4 Bc4 19.Qc2 $16 { 16...Bxe2?? 17.Qxe2 Bxd4 18.Rd5+- and ...Bxe3 does not come with a check now! } )
