17. e5 {[%mdl 32768]} { This position looks promising for White and it is really unfortunate that engine manages to find a path to approximate equality. Still, if unprepared, this position could be really unpleasant to play with Black. White's center is very strong and Black's kingside is weakened. Also, 16... Bc7 is not an easy move to play. } Rb8! {[%cal Gb7b5]} { Black must go for ...b5. } 
18. a4 a6 
