25. Rxf4+ Qxf4 
26. Qd8 { This seems like a decent try for White. It is not possible to develop the queenside for now and Black's king is wide in the open. } Rb8?! { A human move, which runs into trouble. } 
27. h3! Bd7□ 
28. Qxd7+ Kg5 
