23. f4 ( 23.Rxg2 { allows Black to get some counterplay: } 23...Nh4 24.Rf2 Ng5 25.Kh1 Nh3 26.Rff1 Qc7 { and here Black can force a draw: } 27.Nf5 Qxc1 28.Rxc1 Rxc1 29.Qb5 Nf2+ 30.Kg1 Nh3 $14 { . } ) Nh4 
24. f5 Ng5 
