5. Nge2 d5 ( 5...b6 { transposes to 4... b6, but line with c5 which is generally regarded as not that good for Black. } ) ( 5...Nc6 6.a3 Bxc3+ 7.Nxc3 cxd4 8.exd4 d5 9.c5 { should transpose, sooner or later, to the mainline. } ) ( 5...O-O 6.a3 Bxc3+ 7.Nxc3 cxd4 8.exd4 d5 9.c5 { transposes back to @@StartFEN@@rnbqk2r/pp1p1ppp/4pn2/2p5/1bPP4/2N1P3/PP2NPPP/R1BQKB1R b KQkq - 1 5@@EndFEN@@ 5...cxd4 6.exd4 O-O 7.a3 Bxc3 8.Nxc3 d5 9.c5 . } ) 
