9. Ng3 Nxc5 
10. Bxc4 -- ( { This seems to be equal, but White's pieces are coming pretty quickly to the game and Black is under some pressure, e.g. } 10...Bc7 11.Qc2 O-O 12.Rd1 Qe7 13.b4 Ncd7 14.Nce4 $14 )
*

