14. Bg5 g6 
15. Rad1 $16  {[%cal Gc2b3,Gb3a4,Gg5h6,Yd4d5,Gd3h3,Ge2f4][%csl Gc3,Gd3,Gc2,Gd1,Ge1,Gg5,Ge2]} { Black's passive setup has allowed White to get anything he can hope for. All our pieces are beautifully placed - this is a dream scenario for us. We have many plans available, mainly a kingside attack with Bh6 and Qh3 or pressing on the center with Bb3 or even Ba4. Our e2-knight can jump to f4 and a timely d5-break is in the cards. } *

